episodes.title: Trivia Finale: Who Knows More about Tech?
episodes.description:
It's trivia time! This is the conclusion of Season 2 of trivia where we hit Marques, Andrew, and David with a ton of different kinds of questions to see who knows the most about technology (and other random things). We'll be back next week with a regular news-filled episode but for now we hope you play along and maybe learn a thing or two!

currentEpisode.description:
